Package ee.adit.ws.endpoint Description

Web service endpoints (i.e. classes that process web service requests). Contains abstract classes that provide common tasks such as logging the request, preliminary validations, X-Tee specific data validation etc. and also concrete implementing classes. Each endpoint class implements a specific request (a request can have multiple versions).
